              "id": "attend-card-grid",
              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr)); gap:20px;\"><div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; padding:24px; transition:all 0.2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:25.6px; margin-bottom:10.4px;\">📄</div><h4 style=\"font-size:15.2px; color:#0b2545; margin-bottom:6.4px; font-family:Montserrat; font-weight:700;\">Business Owners Without a Draft</h4><p style=\"font-size:13.1px; color:#475569; line-height:1.55;\">If you have not yet begun writing your Personal Narrative, this summit will help you build from the ground up with structured facilitation.</p></div><div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; padding:24px; transition:all 0.2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:25.6px; margin-bottom:10.4px;\">✏️</div><h4 style=\"font-size:15.2px; color:#0b2545; margin-bottom:6.4px; font-family:Montserrat; font-weight:700;\">Business Owners With an Early Draft</h4><p style=\"font-size:13.1px; color:#475569; line-height:1.55;\">If you have a rough draft but feel uncertain about structure, clarity, or completeness, the summit will help you strengthen and organize your narrative.</p></div><div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; padding:24px; transition:all 0.2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:25.6px; margin-bottom:10.4px;\">❓</div><h4 style=\"font-size:15.2px; color:#0b2545; margin-bottom:6.4px; font-family:Montserrat; font-weight:700;\">Owners Unclear on Requirements</h4><p style=\"font-size:13.1px; color:#475569; line-height:1.55;\">If the new DOT Personal Narrative requirements feel confusing or overwhelming, the summit provides practical, plain-language guidance on what is needed and why.</p></div><div style=\"background:#fff; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; padding:24px; transition:all 0.2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:25.6px; margin-bottom:10.4px;\">📋</div><h4 style=\"font-size:15.2px; color:#0b2545; margin-bottom:6.4px; font-family:Montserrat; font-weight:700;\">DBE &amp; ACDBE Certified Business Owners</h4><p style=\"font-size:13.1px; color:#475569; line-height:1.55;\">The summit is specifically designed for current DBE and ACDBE certified business owners navigating the reevaluation process under updated DOT requirements.</p></div></div>"
